# DISTINCT EMAILS ACCROSS 3 PERSON SYSTEMS
# By Mike Aubry Dec 2020 - March 2021# A = OXYGEN IDENTITY
# B = SFDC CONTACT
# C = MARKETO LEADS# Install Eulerr
# https://github.com/jolars/eulerr
# install.packages("eulerr")
library(eulerr)#
Warning: package ‘eulerr’ was built under R version 4.1.1
# FILTERS
## 12/14/2020
# Filters
EMAILS <- c(
        "A" = 3830029,
        "B" = 23063945,
        "C" = 1258443,
        "A&B" = 86876346,
        "A&C" = 111654,
        "B&C" = 4577838,
        "A&B&C" = 12506770
        )
plot(venn(EMAILS))

plot(euler(EMAILS, shape = "ellipse"), quantities = TRUE)
